cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use Whisper (whisper_labia) in your research, please cite it."
title: "Whisper (whisper_labia): Bayesian model comparison of transient light curves"
abstract: >-
  Whisper is an open-source, extensible Python toolkit for Bayesian model comparison of astronomical
  transient light curves: load photometry, fit candidate models with pluggable samplers (ABC, ABC-SMC,
  SNPE), and obtain posteriors plus model-selection metrics (AIC, BIC, max-likelihood).
type: software
authors:
